Package: ThermogramForge
Title: Interactive Thermal Liquid Biopsy Thermogram Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Reger", , "kcr28@nau.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-4312-7844"))
Description: An R Shiny web application for analyzing thermal liquid biopsy (TLB) 
    thermogram data. Provides interactive baseline endpoint detection and adjustment,
    automated signal quality detection, comprehensive metric calculation, and 
    report generation. Integrates with ThermogramBaseline and tlbparam packages
    for all computational analysis.
